  <brief_title>(Valerian) for Improving Sleep in Patients With Cancer Receiving Adjuvant Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Use Of Valeriana Officinalis (Valerian) In Improving Sleep In Patients Who Are Undergoing Adjuvant Treatment For Cancer&quot; A Phase III Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double-Blind Study</official_title>
